Metadata: Use of 1H-15N PEP-HSQC-TOCSY at natural abundance to facilitate the structure elucidation of naturally occurring peptides

The application of inverse detected 15-N NMR spectroscopy is demonstrated here on a 13 mM sample of the biologically active linear tetradecapeptid​e bombesin as a way to expedite the structural characterizatio​n of peptidic natural products.
